data.text: @snarkywench Lymph node pain and swelling is a reaction for some peeps, yes. I wasn't worried until it didn't go away and then had to go to Dr. Out of curiosity, did you also have the weird metal taste straight after the shot?

@snarkywench Oh no! Let me know how you go. I had such bad jaw/saliva gland reaction to the first jab I can’t get the second one.
